         <abstract id="aspace_a0e2c7a46af27ca39e1d793a28613a86">The records consist of minutes, sermons, a visitors register, and bulletins documenting the activities of the Church of Christ in Yale University. Also included are the records of Charles Krigbaum, university organist and choir director.</abstract>
